               Earl begins his prison sentence and finds that life behind 
        bars is not easy and must find the best way of coping with

        attempts, finally finds a way to pay Earl back -- she 
        decides to take care of Randy for him. Meanwhile, Randy 
        has difficulty adjusting to life without Earl and Earl is 
        sought out by a prison bully.
